* Steps to run postman collection  -
    install git client
    install nodejs
    open new Git bash CLI
    npm i â€“g newman (install new man)
    script_folder> newman run <script_file_name json collection file>

* command to run collection
    newman run Day1.postman_collection.json --env-var "baseURL=https://api.restful-api.dev"

* to export result in html install html reporter
    npm install newman-reporter-html -g

* command to export collection result to html
    newman run Day1.postman_collection.json --env-var "baseURL=https://api.restful-api.dev" --reporters html

* command to pass json input data file to collection request
    newman run Day1.postman_collection.json --folder AddObject --env-var "baseURL=https://api.restful-api.dev" --reporters html -d inputData.json


