## Performance testing
>>npm i -g json-server (installing json server)
>> create server.json in project d
>>json-server server.json (run the server)
>>we can add datato server.json using postman or jMeter by adding httpRequest

### performance testing using jMeter
>> install JMeter Apache
>> command to run jmeter file using bash command
>>jmeter -n -l result.jtl -o report -e -t JMeterRequests.jmx